ca-Waves-and-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Mark-Holloway-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Circa Waves 和 The Prodigy。图片来源：Joseph Okpako 和 Mark Holloway，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Circa-Waves-and-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Mark-Holloway-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Circa-Waves-and-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Mark-Holloway-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Circa-Waves-and-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Mark-Holloway-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Circa-Waves-and-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Mark-Holloway-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Circa-Waves-and-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Mark-Holloway-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Circa-Waves-and-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-and-Mark-Holloway-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Circa-Waves">Circa Waves</a>差点错过了本周末在德国举办的音乐节，但<a href="/artists/The-Prodigy">The Prodigy</a>出人意料地出手相救，让他们得救了。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/circa-waves-new-album-never-going-under-interview-2022-rock-3379646">Circa Waves 谈论他们新专辑的“欣快的韧性”并拒绝成为“遗产表演”</a></strong></li></ul><p> “T 恤天气”乐队是受到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/global-it-outage-causes-major-disruption-as-uk-tv-radio-broadcasting-channels-go-offline-3776293">全球 IT 中断</a>影响的众多人之一。此次中断是网络安全公司 Crowd Strike 的一次更新导致全球超过 800 万台计算机崩溃，其中包括世界各地机场使用的设备。</p><p> Circa Waves 正在参加夏季音乐节，并计划于周六（7 月 20 日）在德国 Deichbrand 音乐节上演出。由于 IT 中断，独立乐队不得不取消在庆典上的亮相，直到 The Prodigy 驾驶私人飞机前来救援。</p><p>当晚，这支英国电子乐队也在戴希布兰德音乐节上作为头条表演。他们向 Circa Waves 提供了他们的飞机，利物浦集团接受了。 </p><figure id="attachment_3776933" aria-describedby="